---

<MainLayout>
  <div class="prose text-center mb-4 mx-auto">
    When doing personal work I like to take on projects involving series of
    images connected by a common theme. The result takes on various form,
    ranging from collections of works to graphic novels and zines.
  </div>
  <Heading> SERIES </Heading>
  <div
    class="mx-16 mb-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:gap-2 md:grid-cols-2 items-center justify-between"
  >
    <div>
      <a href="funky-animals">
        <Image
          src={funky}
          alt="main image"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </a>
    </div>
    <a href="mother3">
      <Image src={m3} alt="main image" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
    </a>
  </div>
  <Heading> INDIVISUAL PIECES </Heading>
</MainLayout>
